{"id":152717,"type":1,"name":"タイガーブックス","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/6d/f2/152717_9G7oi.jpg","summary":"辑录了多年间在杂志上所发表的短篇作品，以“虎之书”系列出版。在形态上与“莱欧物语”有许多相似之处，但此书收录的故事，则是以动物为主角的想象作品和一连串具民间传奇色彩的故事为主。此系列并以温馨深情为基调，有血有泪的情节，温柔感伤的场面，在系列中俯拾可得。是以在此系列中的一些作品，一直被视为日本漫画史的经典，改编成动画的也为数甚多。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>虎之书</li><li><span>册数: </span>8</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/1318\">手塚治虫</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/128\">講談社</a>、<a href=\"/person/8365\">時報文化</a>、<a href=\"/person/8050\">文化傳信</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>手塚治虫怪异漫画</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":3,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"「X」","count":1},{"name":"全八卷","count":1},{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"漫画系列","count":1},{"name":"短篇集","count":1},{"name":"手冢治虫","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":1318,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/76/cf/1318_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"手冢治虫","desc":"作者"},{"id":128,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2f/b1/128_prsn_nHh14.jpg","name":"讲谈社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8365,"image":"","name":"台湾时报文化","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8050,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/af/d7/8050_prsn_VkR3u.jpg","name":"文化传信集团有限公司","desc":"出版社"}],"relations":[{"id":77995,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ed/e9/77995_Ma36o.jpg","title":"手塚治虫 THE BEST","type":"不同版本","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/77995"},{"id":122114,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/93/1b/122114_r6Imm.jpg","title":"手塚治虫恐怖短編集","type":"不同版本","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/122114"}],"comic":[{"id":152718,"name":"タイガーブックス (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ac/87/152718_jp.jpg"},{"id":152719,"name":"タイガーブックス (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/e4/84/152719_jp.jpg"},{"id":152720,"name":"タイガーブックス (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/44/54/152720_jp.jpg"},{"id":152721,"name":"タイガーブックス (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ad/00/152721_jp.jpg"},{"id":152722,"name":"タイガーブックス (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/38/b2/152722_jp.jpg"},{"id":152723,"name":"タイガーブックス (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/04/69/152723_jp.jpg"},{